           SPELL=ddclient
         VERSION=3.6.2
          SOURCE=$SPELL-$VERSION.tar.gz
SOURCE_DIRECTORY=$BUILD_DIRECTORY/$SPELL-$VERSION
   SOURCE_URL[0]=http://burry.ca:4141/ddclient/$SOURCE
        WEB_SITE=http://burry.ca:4141/ddclient/
         ENTERED=20020423
         UPDATED=20020423
      MAINTAINER=djcomputer@gmx.net
           SHORT="client for some dynamic DNS services"
cat << EOF
ddclient is a Perl client used to update dynamic DNS
entries for accounts on many dynamic DNS services.

Dynamic DNS services currently supported include:

DynDNS.org - See http://www.dyndns.org for details on
             obtaining a free account.
Hammernode - See http://www.hn.org for details on obtaining
             a free account.
Zoneedit   - See http://www.zoneedit.com for details.
EasyDNS    - See http://www.easydns.com for details.

Also include is support for DSL Reports host monitoring
service. [Highly recommended]
See http://dslreports.com for details.

DDclient now supports many of cable/dsl broadband routers.
EOF
